Ubuntu install
--------------

1. Installing requirements

Run in a text console the following commands:

sudo apt-get install exiv2 ffmpeg graphicsmagick python3 python3-pip
cd <liveblog_dir>
sudo pip install -r requirements.txt

Replace <liveblog_dir> with the directory where you unarchived the contents
of the Liveblog package.


2. Generate configuration files

Run in the same console the following command:

python3 application.py -dump
cp -f plugins-linux.properties plugins.properties


3. Run the Liveblog server:

python3 application.py


4. Open the Liveblog user interface in a browser from the following URL:

http://localhost:8080/content/lib/core/start.html
